digiKam 8.2.0 - Release date: 2023-12-03

*****************************************************************************************************
NEW FEATURES:

Libraw : Update to snapshot 2023-11-21.
Bundles: MacOS PKG is now based on Qt framework 5.15.11 and KDE frameworks 5.110.
Bundles: Linux AppImage is now based on Qt framework 5.15.11 and KDE frameworks 5.110.
Bundles: Windows installer is now based on Qt framework 5.15.11 and KDE frameworks 5.110.
Bundles: New Windows installer compiled under Windows with VCPKG tool-chain and based on Qt6 and KF6 frameworks.
Bundles: Exiftool updated to last 12.70.
Bundles: Exiv2 updated to last 0.28.1.

*****************************************************************************************************
